                  <summary>1 copy of Hidāyat al-aʿmá by Ḥusayn Kashmīrī</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2006003807 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008104964" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1573x-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian, Arabic</textLang>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_9432">Hidāyat al-aʿmá</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_9432">هداية الاعمىٰ</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Systematic treatise on the importance of ethics in Sufism, by <persName key="person_f5459" role="aut">Ḥusayn [ibn Zīnat va Zayn] Kashmīrī</persName>, about whom little is known. 
                        </p>
                        <p>The treatise is divided into eighteen sections termed bāb. 
</p>
                        <p>Not dated at end. 
</p>
                        <p>Elegant naskh in ruled frames and initially stained text panels; Arabic passages and quotations overlined in red ink. 
</p>
                        <p>Paper wrapper. 
</p>
                        <p>Folios partially bound; cropped, water and fungal stains, wormholes. 
</p>
                        <p>Condition fragile. 
</p>
                        <p>Condition very poor, especially towards the end. 
</p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f5459">Ḥusayn Kashmīrī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="person_f5459">حسين كشميرى</persName>
                     </author>
                  </msItem>
